<String Id="LaunchApp">Launch LMVideoStudio</String>
<String Id="DowngradeErrorMessage">A newer version of LMVideoStudio is already installed.</String>
<String Id="PathEnvVarFeature">Add the install location of the LMVideoStudio executable to the PATH system environment variable. This allows the LMVideoStudio executable to be called from any location.</String>
<String Id="InstallAppFeature">Installs LMVideoStudio.</String></WixLocalization>
